# Bridges Across Borders Website

This role configures a basic nginx PHP evirnonment. The actual wordpress
sources, database scripts and SSL certificates are managed via the backup
system.

## wp-cli

The tool https://wp-cli.org/ is installed to manage the wordpress instance.

  su bab -c 'wp plugin --path=/var/www/bab/wordpress update --all'
  su bab -c 'wp core --path=/var/www/bab/wordpress update'

